<section id="itsm_taClassRef">
    <title>taClassRef</title>
    
    <para>Text Analysis Class Reference - the <code>taClassRef</code> attribute is the <olink
        targetdoc="../xliff21.xml" targetptr="ITS20">[ITS]</olink> defined <code>taClassRef</code> attribute.</para>
    
    
    <para><emphasis>Value description:</emphasis> IRI</para>
    <para>The IRI is supposed to resolve as human or machine readable <ulink url="http://www.w3.org/TR/its20/#textAnalysis-info-pieces">Entity type / concept class</ulink> information.</para>
    
    <para><emphasis>Default value:</emphasis>: undefined</para>
    
    
    
    <para><emphasis>Used in:</emphasis>
        <olink targetdoc="../../elements/inline/mrk.xml" targetptr="mrk"
            ><code>&lt;mrk></code></olink>, and
        <olink targetdoc="../../elements/inline/sm.xml"
            targetptr="sm"><code>&lt;sm></code></olink>.</para>
    
    <para>See the <olink targetdoc="../../modules/itsm/Text_Analysis.xml" targetptr="taAnnotation">ITS Text Analysis Annotation</olink> for the normative usage description of this attribute. Advanced Constraints follow from that normative usage description.</para>
    
</section>
